{"type": "article", "id": 3791, "title": "石头与陶瓷组合的花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-24T08:18:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233310mkNF2yfIinD9LOjA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙设计师 Martín Azúa 日前携手 Marc Vidal 推出了一系列名为「Vase With Stone」的花瓶，设计师想用这一作品表现出如同石头陨落的瞬间的美感。在制作工艺上，这一系列的花瓶并无多少技巧可言，但陶瓷与岩石的相互作用却唤起了一种原始的力量，石头的位置进行了精巧的设计，仿佛是一股巨大的力量落下，塑造了陶瓷边缘的效果。仅从外形来看，即便没有插入鲜花和绿植，这款花瓶也可以独立成为一个家居空间的装饰品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233308pTXFlNQfmtWsgVd5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233308YQg9Z5ytCLuvMpSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233309dos1zLxMT38fHVy6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233309d3i6T1LhOyp4Hl9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233310Z1eFuAGQ0XtJK3RT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}